Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.41,0:00:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.48,0:00:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.42,0:00:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.76,0:00:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团队的名称保密\N保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.97,0:00:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纠正一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.85,0:00:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是JT团队的优优\N请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.39,0:01:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.67,0:01:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做这个成员2年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.62,0:01:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.76,0:01:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的三围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.90,0:01:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从上面开始88
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.24,0:01:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰围是59
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.98,0:02:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臀围是89
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.25,0:02:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.17,0:02:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小穴\N要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.39,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错，好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的屁股在发抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.58,0:04:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.72,0:05:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.79,0:05:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了,去了,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.06,0:05:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.23,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢看这么淫荡的表演吗\N喜欢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.24,0:06:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.15,0:07:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.66,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请再好好看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.04,0:09:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结衣小姐！才刚开始哦！\N不要太疯狂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.54,0:13:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RQ\N内射不穿内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么淫荡的姐姐RQ\N和结衣小姐在酒店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.08,0:14:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看你穿很多不同风格\N的衣服，制服怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.43,0:15:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服？好淫荡\N你的裙子很短啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.04,0:15:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用那么淫荡的眼神看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.58,0:15:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.78,0:15:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太诱人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有穿过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍摄的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.53,0:15:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常穿那样的衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天穿这样也可以进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.75,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感想很不错吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.09,0:16:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.03,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你绝对是那样想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常位很简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感想很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.91,0:16:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会想到很淫荡的事情\N淫荡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.98,0:16:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你穿这样就只能幻想很淫荡\N的事情，面前有那样的双腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.46,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那样，那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.27,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.40,0:16:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的，你好淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.81,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.55,0:17:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个很诱人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.09,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人的话会很在意女人的\N身体线条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体线条\N会抓住他们的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.10,0:17:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会了，我穿的很普通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.57,0:17:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近很多人这样穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.98,0:17:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么棒的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.52,0:17:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再给我看看你淫荡的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.40,0:17:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再做一下自我介绍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.87,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，好害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.82,0:18:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢拍摄AV
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.69,0:18:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说会洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.96,0:18:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时情侣的话也会洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.97,0:18:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家追求利激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.32,0:18:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很认真观看的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是要给大家看到最好\N的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.80,0:19:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？感觉被欺骗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.83,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.90,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先，首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.04,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最简单的，最基本的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.98,0:19:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢你这样的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.45,0:19:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做为男性的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.19,0:19:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被你捕获了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结衣你实际的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.87,0:20:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.48,0:20:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.69,0:20:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己主动一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.69,0:20:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很变态呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.56,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.44,0:20:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很适合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.04,0:20:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超适合的\N只有这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.25,0:20:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个，那个很适合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.26,0:21:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊\N蕾丝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再配上这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.26,0:21:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错\N是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.14,0:21:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅气，这个好棒\N我想穿上看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以给我看看吗? \N我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去穿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.76,0:21:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换好了请叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.17,0:21:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我换好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.50,0:21:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换好了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,号码大小可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.78,0:22:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个，很紧吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.18,0:22:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么，为什么?\N真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.79,0:22:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.06,0:22:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不小\N就是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.60,0:22:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再转到后面，后面\N后面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好利激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.60,0:22:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太远了，再近一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.48,0:22:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真帅气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.15,0:22:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里比较紧\N这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.42,0:22:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那个形式的\N是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.09,0:22:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.10,0:22:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.57,0:22:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱是很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.44,0:23:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再看这边，看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.72,0:23:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扒开是是吗感觉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.73,0:23:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扒开吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.66,0:23:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再下面一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.60,0:23:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚好的位置\N这里吗？这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.48,0:23:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.16,0:23:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.76,0:23:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太诱人了\N再来，再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.64,0:24:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不错\N真帅气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.97,0:24:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅气\N我好紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.58,0:24:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着这个拍摄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.92,0:24:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗?\N好棒，超适合你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.26,0:24:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超喜欢\N不是吧？是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.60,0:24:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太变态了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.74,0:24:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾丝的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.61,0:24:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该更吸引客人\N真的吗?真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.95,0:24:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会试看看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.09,0:24:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.96,0:24:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走走看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.77,0:25:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你第一次穿这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.71,0:25:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上的衣服还有另一个特点\N特点吗？是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.39,0:25:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不住了\N忍不住了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.13,0:25:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以手淫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.07,0:25:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.28,0:25:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.28,0:25:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个，怎么做\N要怎么使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.89,0:26:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.89,0:26:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以呢\N突然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.50,0:26:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边晃动的比较慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.97,0:26:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.71,0:26:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是配套的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.58,0:26:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一套的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.85,0:26:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.06,0:26:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用看看巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.40,0:26:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.73,0:26:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里，这里\N不行，好淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.41,0:26:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下哦\N一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.61,0:27:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振动棒\N很厉害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.28,0:27:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振动棒和这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.03,0:27:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,权喜欢\N都很喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.96,0:27:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.77,0:27:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不脱掉的话做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.04,0:27:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.38,0:27:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样，这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:33.98,0:27:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，那里\N那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.05,0:27:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个角度好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.19,0:27:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊\N这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:53.20,0:27:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等，一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:58.68,0:28:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，晃动的好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.22,0:28:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，不行\N在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.82,0:28:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么啊？\N突然好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.90,0:28:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢的\N慢慢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.98,0:28:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡\N为什么突然就开始了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:48.19,0:28:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不湿了\N不能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:01.94,0:29:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.29,0:29:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.51,0:29:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，就是那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.99,0:29:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.66,0:29:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.41,0:30:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到乳头吧\N真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.62,0:30:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.96,0:30:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.30,0:30:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.79,0:31:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.47,0:31:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的下面\N水水的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.41,0:31:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉吧\N脱下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.22,0:31:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.36,0:31:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:44.10,0:31:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.70,0:31:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样扔开的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:51.97,0:31:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边也脱下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.52,0:32:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丝袜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.66,0:32:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.20,0:32:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕破吧\N不行吗?不行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:26.68,0:32:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个扒开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.35,0:32:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道要怎么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.69,0:32:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很了解男人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.23,0:32:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:49.37,0:32:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服，我的服装吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.70,0:33:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先脱下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.78,0:33:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再插进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.71,0:33:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样做可以吗？\N是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:08.18,0:33:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做那样的事情吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.46,0:33:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再从上面插进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:27.54,0:33:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进去了\N真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.55,0:33:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.02,0:33:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进去了\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.05,0:34:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全插进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.00,0:34:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.08,0:34:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，好多蜜汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.96,0:34:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？\N看着边，这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:19.25,0:35:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进去了\N全插进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.92,0:35:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗？全看到了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.00,0:35:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插那么深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:47.54,0:35:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以吗?\N可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.48,0:35:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好抽送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.59,0:36:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水水的了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.39,0:36:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.67,0:36:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续抽送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:58.15,0:37:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面\N去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.55,0:37:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.62,0:37:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.69,0:37:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.96,0:37:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.70,0:37:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:30.85,0:37:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了啊\N小穴射了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:34.72,0:37:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.40,0:37:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开双腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:47.66,0:37:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高潮了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:01.14,0:38:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.48,0:38:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进去的地方全看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.96,0:38:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进去的地方很爽吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.97,0:38:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒，在发抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.11,0:38:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒，好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.53,0:38:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽吗?\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:07.34,0:39:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.55,0:39:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抖动的好厉害\N去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.76,0:39:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边，这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.69,0:39:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:41.64,0:39:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.25,0:39:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，真爽，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.12,0:39:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.73,0:40:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.74,0:40:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续吧\N太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:11.14,0:40:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.14,0:40:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了，出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.68,0:40:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.15,0:40:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个插进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:29.03,0:40:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看上面的水水\N好棒，真的好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:48.64,0:40:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:56.65,0:40:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.26,0:41:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.59,0:41:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:05.86,0:41:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.73,0:41:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:22.01,0:41:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样的可能你可能没办法满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.82,0:41:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:30.02,0:41:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.69,0:41:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系，我今天准备了\N很多好玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.10,0:41:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:45.90,0:41:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备了吗?\N没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.31,0:41:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧？\N是可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:03.39,0:42:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴茎吗？阴茎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:05.39,0:42:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要温柔一点\N不可以直接说阴茎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.66,0:42:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要含蓄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.21,0:42:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:34.08,0:42:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要好好表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.42,0:42:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太淫荡了\N因为太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.70,0:42:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振动棒和这个哪个舒服?\N这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:54.10,0:42:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗？是的，超舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.51,0:43:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:02.65,0:43:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.46,0:43:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都没看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:20.93,0:43:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再穿不一样的服装吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.54,0:43:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.87,0:43:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:34.01,0:43:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:47.76,0:43:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果真是个好女人，好淫荡！\N但是只是到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.03,0:43:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说她淫荡的话，说到RQ\N我们只能继续了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:59.10,0:44:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个服装不错\N可以站起来一下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:13.38,0:44:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.79,0:44:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了，来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.92,0:44:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要穿这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.06,0:44:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个很碍事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:29.93,0:44:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.87,0:44:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蕾丝控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:38.21,0:44:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:42.21,0:44:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是女性代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.82,0:44:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看一下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.36,0:44:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她白天玩了玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:00.50,0:45:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有得到两足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:07.04,0:45:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体好淫荡呢\N很淫荡吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:14.24,0:45:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:23.59,0:45:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我插进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.80,0:45:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再碰上去\N喜欢这样吗?很喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:09.23,0:46:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身材真不错\N是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:34.06,0:46:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:37.13,0:46:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的乳头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:40.46,0:46:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很容易摸的乳头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:59.55,0:47:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我摸了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:03.02,0:47:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双腿张开一下\N屁股翘起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:52.79,0:49:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要舔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:12.34,0:51:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.09,0:51:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面很湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:34.89,0:51:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想看看\N很浪费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:45.17,0:51:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样哦\N这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:47.84,0:51:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:10.39,0:52:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:20.67,0:52:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕破了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:32.55,0:52:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:48.76,0:53:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:55.57,0:53:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢这样吧?\N真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:08.11,0:54:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很兴奋吗?\N好兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:27.20,0:54:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.47,0:54:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:36.41,0:54:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:53.09,0:54:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:25.12,0:55:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太兴奋了\N张开的好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:59.82,0:56:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:36.93,0:56:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:08.56,0:57:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:11.36,0:57:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:15.77,0:57:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:53.40,0:57:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不行\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:03.01,0:58:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.74,1:00:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发出声音\N好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:15.01,1:00:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:45.71,1:00:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全插进去了\N好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:22.41,1:01:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:19.67,1:02:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:31.95,1:02:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进来\N好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:38.89,1:02:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:59.58,1:03:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:19.86,1:03:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:28.00,1:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:50.56,1:03:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样?\N阴茎好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.57,1:04:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口水出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:20.99,1:04:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不行\N不要拔出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:28.60,1:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:32.74,1:04:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再转过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:37.54,1:04:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看的更清楚\N坐下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.29,1:04:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:05.44,1:05:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:26.39,1:05:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:41.34,1:05:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:01.49,1:06:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:11.90,1:06:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，真爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:23.78,1:06:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样插进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:02.22,1:07:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:13.30,1:07:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:20.37,1:07:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:35.18,1:07:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:37.99,1:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:40.52,1:07:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:44.19,1:08:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:21.82,1:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗?\N那里好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.72,1:09:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:48.25,1:09:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:14.41,1:10:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:22.95,1:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:33.16,1:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.45,1:12:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扒开小穴好好看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:13.33,1:12:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里喜欢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:30.68,1:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:52.44,1:12:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，不行\N去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:04.98,1:13:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:23.93,1:13:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:26.20,1:13:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不行\N去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:30.74,1:13:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:37.81,1:13:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:00.10,1:14:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了，射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:39.67,1:15:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了\N太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:44.87,1:15:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的太舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:48.88,1:15:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会怀孕吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:54.88,1:15:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:58.62,1:16:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:13.97,1:16:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:28.12,1:16:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:32.92,1:16:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:41.20,1:16:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边吧\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:47.07,1:16:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黏黏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:52.28,1:16:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黏黏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:54.28,1:16:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:57.88,1:17:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:06.69,1:17:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然服装被撕破,但是\N还有视觉盛宴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:10.56,1:17:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结衣会更好的满足我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:14.43,1:17:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几天后，结衣跟我们联系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:18.84,1:17:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还是很久前的话题了\N但还是不满足的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:21.90,1:17:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:25.11,1:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗?\N这边也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:32.05,1:17:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:34.72,1:17:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新衣服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:41.12,1:17:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，这个是制服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:46.73,1:17:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了，这里\N全看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:51.00,1:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个可以吗?\N这里被看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:57.41,1:18:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总穿这样吗?\N会被抓住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:01.28,1:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住\N不会的，没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:05.82,1:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:10.22,1:18:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有遮掩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:23.30,1:18:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样，这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:27.17,1:18:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:34.38,1:18:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你穿这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:41.18,1:18:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常的紧张\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:45.32,1:18:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直等待你的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:52.26,1:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？真的\N今天还穿这么漂亮，适合我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:01.87,1:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合\N下面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:05.88,1:19:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有\N直接的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:10.81,1:19:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接吗\N直接
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:14.28,1:19:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接穿的话我可以看出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:20.82,1:19:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:24.03,1:19:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手扒开看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:29.90,1:19:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全看到了\N看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:33.50,1:19:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太诱人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:38.04,1:19:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都穿这样\N是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:42.31,1:19:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太令人心动了\N是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:03.53,1:20:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比较私人的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:14.74,1:20:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你平时穿什么样的衣服?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:20.75,1:20:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:24.09,1:20:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:31.96,1:20:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通啊\N要怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:40.90,1:20:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想了解一下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:51.05,1:20:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超想看\N真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:04.66,1:21:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不行，那不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:09.87,1:21:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会用玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:16.01,1:21:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的话用手指就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.48,1:21:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让你兴奋的\N真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:28.95,1:21:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:33.49,1:21:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起约会\N有男友吗?没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:37.89,1:21:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的没男友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:48.71,1:21:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:57.25,1:22:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有男友吗？\N男友吗?就在我面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:04.99,1:22:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男友在我面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:27.14,1:22:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:32.22,1:22:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有，一定有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:36.09,1:22:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天说的就2个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:45.43,1:22:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要插入
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:51.43,1:22:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:54.90,1:23:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的是密室里面就只有2个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:01.18,1:23:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样的感觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:04.65,1:23:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想你尝试一下怎么样?\N做做看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:09.85,1:23:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:13.06,1:23:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了\N不然还会和谁?不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.46,1:23:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一下就不可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:24.13,1:23:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行\N真的不可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:28.54,1:23:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我不可以啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:35.88,1:23:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:40.28,1:23:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会哭\N绝对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:46.16,1:23:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没关系\N我想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:55.77,1:23:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:04.31,1:24:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能说完可以2分钟就会射精\N好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:10.05,1:24:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害什么都没做就射精吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:16.99,1:24:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是看一下就会射精\N好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:21.52,1:24:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:29.67,1:24:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妁要坚持和习惯一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:33.67,1:24:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一样的体验
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:38.21,1:24:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是完全不一样的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:48.89,1:24:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有我的帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:55.02,1:24:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:01.16,1:25:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:05.84,1:25:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新体验啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:12.24,1:25:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没尝试过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:16.91,1:25:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好体验一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:21.98,1:25:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫他进来\N可以吧?没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:27.06,1:25:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就在外面吗?\N在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:31.46,1:25:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会进来\N不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:34.26,1:25:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在外面等N不是吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:38.94,1:25:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫他进来吧\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:41.34,1:25:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:46.54,1:25:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在那边的\N不在吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:51.08,1:25:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没来啊\N拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:58.69,1:26:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没来\N真的在那里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:09.50,1:26:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己叫一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:14.70,1:26:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了\N男优拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:23.38,1:26:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的，真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:25.78,1:26:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了，突然的\N这么积极啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:38.06,1:26:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:40.86,1:26:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:48.60,1:26:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的，真人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:52.21,1:27:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也是真人\N我是蕾丝控
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:00.48,1:27:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:04.89,1:27:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不一样的感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.16,1:27:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗?\N是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:13.83,1:27:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个很糟糕，穿胸罩了吗?\N没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:21.30,1:27:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真空吧?\N大家都不穿的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:24.91,1:27:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不穿吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:28.11,1:27:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是，大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:32.25,1:27:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的，是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:35.59,1:27:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没胸罩\N乳峰是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:41.99,1:27:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是吧\N不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:49.73,1:27:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面，下面呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:54.94,1:27:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都看到内裤了\N内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:02.95,1:28:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个会被拍到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:06.15,1:28:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会这么近距离的拍摄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:10.29,1:28:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:17.49,1:28:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时在外面有人偷拍的\N不知道吗?我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:22.30,1:28:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:24.57,1:28:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我检查一下\N出来了，没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:29.51,1:28:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然处理过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:32.98,1:28:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还是出来了\N真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:37.51,1:28:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:40.45,1:28:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:45.39,1:28:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是什么？\N很晋通的这样的绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:53.00,1:28:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个下面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:57.53,1:29:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么遮掩的东西吧\N没穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:05.94,1:29:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样啊\N那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:13.82,1:29:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?\N是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:17.29,1:29:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都穿这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:22.09,1:29:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾丝的话我完全看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:30.50,1:29:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸了的话很快会很舒服吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:37.97,1:29:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被摸吧\N不会的，那样会抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:49.45,1:29:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能有吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:55.86,1:29:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:06.54,1:30:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一件啊\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:15.08,1:30:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:25.49,1:30:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，肌肤滑滑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:28.96,1:30:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:36.03,1:30:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:40.17,1:30:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:22.75,1:31:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了\N全看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:04.92,1:32:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:13.60,1:32:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱掉可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:17.60,1:32:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，胸部真不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:28.41,1:32:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从上面和下面都能看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:38.15,1:32:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适合我吗?\N很适合
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:46.70,1:32:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:52.97,1:32:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心，很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:56.17,1:33:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样摸的话我很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:45.29,1:33:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开双腿给我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:50.09,1:33:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:59.84,1:34:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:03.71,1:34:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:06.78,1:34:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能遮掩住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:16.79,1:34:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好淫荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:22.13,1:34:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了，全看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:47.35,1:34:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双腿真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:03.23,1:35:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，全夹紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:14.44,1:35:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?好舒服\N舒服吗?内裤夹紧了舒服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:48.21,1:35:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:55.95,1:35:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:11.70,1:36:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒，这个好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:14.77,1:36:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全夹住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:19.71,1:36:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:25.98,1:36:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了\N全夹紧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:43.47,1:36:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:49.07,1:36:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以看下小穴吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:52.14,1:36:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:09.36,1:37:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡，全看到了呢\N你的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:16.97,1:37:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:20.30,1:37:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?\N真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:24.84,1:37:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想仔细的看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:35.39,1:37:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:37.92,1:37:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拿回去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:42.73,1:37:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:46.33,1:37:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗? \N那撕破了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:12.49,1:38:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:15.16,1:38:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全扒开了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:19.16,1:38:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:22.77,1:38:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿再抬起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:27.57,1:38:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花瓣打开\N也看到屁眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:34.11,1:38:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，不可以\N给我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:07.08,1:39:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N好淫荡的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:20.42,1:39:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:23.09,1:39:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了\N要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:29.90,1:39:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样玩弄小穴很舒服吧\N好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:46.45,1:39:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，不行，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:49.39,1:39:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了，去了，去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:18.61,1:40:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴全看到了
